{"tid":1214299,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"金鐘踩單車注意事項及裝備","createTime":"2019-06-13T04:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T08:30:40.000Z","uid":39182,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e68e9fa7e0771633b2f45728b6dd08e8e0552bb","tid":1214299,"uid":39182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:01:00.000Z","msg":"首先, 馬路上踩單車係合法既, 歡迎大家做路權L  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/road_users_code/index/chapter_4_for_cyclists/cycling_/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Froad_safety%2Froad_users_code%2Findex%2Fchapter_4_for_cyclists%2Fcycling_%2Findex.html&d=lXSk0n6jiDV9AqJ6X6RhLqF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=ebdeb0a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/road_users_code/index/chapter_4_for_cyclists/cycling_/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n單車好貴或者唔方便帶出去? 唔緊要我地有好先進既共享單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n單車可以出去先借，但裝備就當然要自己帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係馬路上皮包鐵始終危險，所以全副裝備都好重要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6KE89N3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6KE89N3.jpg&h=ef73da92&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n加上市區空氣污染嚴重，配合埋過濾能力強既口睪，咁就可以保護自己之餘又可以散熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家踩單車強身健體去金鐘野餐，又可以支持環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b0f9c3835787e50425d81c766f7ded559d604d","tid":1214299,"uid":39182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:22:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76f81aa622b6d771e73644f83623ae5ce45dcf63","tid":1214299,"uid":39182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:41:59.000Z","msg":"再推<br />\n<br />\n俾多D 人知要咩安全配備"},{"pid":"1a1d76cf0a6820e